          "text": "Al-Harawī, Muḥammad Mīr Zāhid. Minhuwāt-al-Shāriḥ al-Jalāl-al-Dawānī & Al-Ḥawāshī al-Zahidiyya ‘alā Sharḥ-al-Hayākil. In Al-Dawānī, Jalāl-al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn-As‘ad al-Ṣiddīqī. Shawākil-al-Ḥūr fī Sharḥ Hayākil-al-Nūr li-Shaykh al-Ishrāq al-Shihāb al-Suhrawardī. Including al-Harawī, Muḥammad Mīr Zāhid, Minhuwāt-al-Shāriḥ al-Jalāl-al-Dawānī & Al-Ḥawāshī al-Zahidiyya ‘alā Sharḥ-al-Hayākil. Amman: Dār-al-Fatḥ, 1444/2023."
