          "text": "Ibn-‘Arabī, [Muḥyī-al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn-‘Alī al-Ḥātimī al-Ṭā’ī]. Al-Ajwiba al-Lā’iqa ‘an al-As’ila al-Fā’iqa; Al-Maqṣid al-Asmā fī al-Ishārāt fī-Mā Waqa‘a fī al-Qur’ān bi Lisān-al-Ḥaqīqa wa al-Sharī‘a min al-Kināyāt; Al-Muqni‘ fī al-Sahl al-Mumtani‘; Al-Ḥaqq fī al-Nu‘ūt wa al-Asmā’ al-Ilāhiyya. Edited by Amīn Ḥamdī al-Akbarī and ‘Alī Jumu‘a. N.p.: Mu’assasat-Ibn-‘Arabī, 2021."
