          "text": "Al-Malījī, Abū-al-Uns Muḥyī-al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn-‘Abd-al-Raḥmān. Al-Sirr al-Rabbānī fī-Ma‘rifat-Ṭarīqat-al-Sha‘rānī. Including Al-Sha‘rānī, ‘Abd-al-Wahhāb ibn-Aḥmad, Adab-al-Murīd al-Ṣādiq ma‘a Man Urīdu al-Khāliq; Mawāzīn-al-Rijāl al-Qāṣirīn; Mawā‘iẓ-al-Zabūr; Marwiyyāt-al-Imām al-Sha‘rānī ‘an-al-Jalāl al-Suyūṭī. Edited by Muḥammad ‘Abd-al-Qādir Naṣṣār. Cairo: Dār-al-Iḥsān, 2025."
