          "text": "———. Ennead IV: On the Essence of the Soul I & II; On the Difficulties of the Soul I-III; On Sight; On Sense-Perception and Memory; On the Immortality of the Soul; On the Descent of the Soul into Bodies; If all Souls are One. Translated by A. H. Armstrong. Loeb Classical Library Series on Plotinus: Book IV. Cambridge, MA & London, England: Harvard University Press, 1984."
